(14782, 14742, 'themo_html_1_content', '<table style=\"height: 124px; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 40%;\">\n<h3>Physical Environment</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"> </td>\n<td>\n<h3>Multitenancy Isolation</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p>LinovHR using  <a href=\"https://d0.awsstatic.com/whitepapers/aws-security-whitepaper.pdf\">Amazon Web Service</a>  as cloud provider. What is that mean? world class physical facility, security and control management. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fire detection and suppression</li>\n<li>Fully redundant electrical power systems.</li>\n<li>Climate and temperature control</li>\n<li>Standard process of storage device decommissioning</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p> You can rest assured on your data privacy. We implement 3 layers isolation :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Application</li>\n<li>Database</li>\n<li>Host url</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49%;\">\n<h3>Network and Data</h3>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 49%;\">\n<h3>Host</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Secure protocol for web dan  data delivery (HTTPS)</li>\n<li>Private connection</li>\n<li>Multi layers firewall</li>\n<li>Sensitive data stored encrypted</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Updated antivirus and antimalware</li>\n<li>SSL configurated to use powerful encryption algorithm such as AES-256</li>\n<li>Resource usage monitoring</li>\n<li>Remote access restriction</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49%;\">\n<h3>Application</h3>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 49%;\">\n<h3>Data Access</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Engine patching and update</li>\n<li>Sql injection prevention</li>\n<li>Cross site scripting prevention</li>\n<li>File upload filtering</li>\n<li>Audit trail</li>\n<li>Captcha</li>\n<li>Lockout feature</li>\n<li>Hardening web dan database server</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 49%; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>User login</li>\n<li>Password policy</li>\n<li>Group role and management</li>\n<li>Tokenized user session management</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n'),
